BBQ Champ UK - Series 1, Episode 4




It's the semi-final and just five BBQers remain in the hunt as the stakes are high in the 'BBQ HQ Challenge' where they must each create a full Sunday lunch on the grill. Then it's time for the BBQers to head to the International Street Food Market in Camden to test their skills on the Yakitori grill and the flavours of the East.




Original Air Date: 21-Aug-2015
